{"id":309597665,"lang":"python","lang_name":"Python","time":"3 years, 6 months","timestamp":1583419779,"status":15,"status_display":"Runtime Error","runtime":"N/A","url":"/submissions/detail/309597665/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"String to Integer (atoi)","memory":"N/A","code":"class Solution(object):\n    def myAtoi(self, s):\n        \"\"\"\n        :type str: str\n        :rtype: int\n        \"\"\"\n        s = s.strip()\n        length = len(s)\n        res = \"\"\n        i = 0\n        # 以字母开头是不合法的，以'+', '-'和数字开头是合法的\n        while length > 0:\n            if ((i == 0) and (s[i] == '+' or s[i] == '-' or s[i].isdigit())) \\\n                or ((i > 0) and s[i].isdigit()):\n                i += 1\n                res.append(s[i])\n                length -= 1\n            else:\n                break\n        # 如果一个数字都没找到或者只找到一个'+'或'-'，那么是不合法的\n        if len(res) == 0 or (len(res) == 1 and (s[i] == '+' or s[i] == '-')):\n            return 0\n        else:\n             ans = int(res)\n        if ans > pow(2,31)-1:\n            return pow(2,31)-1\n        elif ans < -pow(2,31):\n            return -pow(2,31)\n        else:\n            return ans","compare_result":"","title_slug":"string-to-integer-atoi","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
